Introduction

Yoona is a South Korean singer under STARON Entertainment. In 2023, Yoona participated in the SBS survival show "Universe Ticket" where she finished 6th place, securing her spot as a member of the South Korean project girl group UNIS.

Yoona debuted as a member of UNIS on March 27, 2024, with their first mini-album "WE UNIS" and the title track "SUPERWOMAN."

Yoona was previously a member of the upcoming girl group Free In Sass and a former member of the kids co-ed group Play With Me Club.
